DTSTART:20260708T180000
DTEND:20260708T210000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing
LOCATION:Studio Two Three\, 109 W 15th St\, Richmond\, VA 23224
DESCRIPTION:3-hour figure drawing workshop with a professional nude model. Poses called by instructor Carter Helmandollar\, beginning with short gestural poses and concluding with longer poses. Bring your own drawing/painting/sculpting materials (extra paper\, pencils\, and clipboards available).\\n\\nCost: $20\\n\\nRegister: https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-78
URL:https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-78
END:VEVENT
